      "7": "That|strong=\"G2443\"the|strong=\"G3588\"trial of|strong=\"G1223\"your|strong=\"G2532\"faith|strong=\"G4102\"(much more|strong=\"G4186\"precious|strong=\"G4186\"than|strong=\"G2532\"gold|strong=\"G5553\"which|strong=\"G3588\"is|strong=\"G3588\"tried by|strong=\"G1722\"the|strong=\"G3588\"fire|strong=\"G4442\") may|strong=\"G2532\"be|strong=\"G2532\"found|strong=\"G2147\"unto praise|strong=\"G1868\"and|strong=\"G2532\"glory|strong=\"G1391\"and|strong=\"G2532\"honour at|strong=\"G1722\"the|strong=\"G3588\"appearing of|strong=\"G1223\"Jesus|strong=\"G2424\"Christ|strong=\"G5547\":",
