      "9": "Receiving|strong=\"G2865\"the|strong=\"G3588\"end|strong=\"G5056\"of|strong=\"G3588\"your|strong=\"G4102\"faith|strong=\"G4102\", even the|strong=\"G3588\"salvation|strong=\"G4991\"of|strong=\"G3588\"your|strong=\"G4102\"souls|strong=\"G5590\".",
