      "11": "Searching what|strong=\"G5101\"or|strong=\"G2228\"what|strong=\"G5101\"manner of|strong=\"G4151\"time|strong=\"G2540\"the|strong=\"G3588\"Spirit|strong=\"G4151\"of|strong=\"G4151\"Christ|strong=\"G5547\"in|strong=\"G1722\"them|strong=\"G0846\"did|strong=\"G2228\"signify: when|strong=\"G2532\"it|strong=\"G0846\"foretold those|strong=\"G3588\"sufferings|strong=\"G3804\"that|strong=\"G3778\"are|strong=\"G3778\"in|strong=\"G1722\"Christ|strong=\"G5547\", and|strong=\"G2532\"the|strong=\"G3588\"glories|strong=\"G1391\"that|strong=\"G3778\"should|strong=\"G3778\"follow:",
      "12": "To|strong=\"G1519\"whom|strong=\"G3739\"it|strong=\"G0846\"was|strong=\"G3739\"revealed|strong=\"G0601\", that|strong=\"G3754\"not|strong=\"G3756\"to|strong=\"G1519\"themselves|strong=\"G1438\", but|strong=\"G1161\"to|strong=\"G1519\"you|strong=\"G5210\"they|strong=\"G0846\"ministered|strong=\"G1247\"those|strong=\"G3588\"things|strong=\"G3739\"which|strong=\"G3739\"are|strong=\"G3739\"now|strong=\"G1161\"declared to|strong=\"G1519\"you|strong=\"G5210\"by|strong=\"G1722\"them|strong=\"G0846\"that|strong=\"G3754\"have|strong=\"G3748\"preached|strong=\"G2097\"the|strong=\"G3588\"gospel|strong=\"G2097\"to|strong=\"G1519\"you|strong=\"G5210\", the|strong=\"G3588\"Holy|strong=\"G0040\"Ghost being|strong=\"G4771\"sent|strong=\"G0649\"down from|strong=\"G0575\"heaven|strong=\"G3772\", on|strong=\"G1722\"whom|strong=\"G3739\"the|strong=\"G3588\"angels|strong=\"G0032\"desire|strong=\"G1937\"to|strong=\"G1519\"look|strong=\"G3879\".",
      "13": "Wherefore|strong=\"G1352\"having the|strong=\"G3588\"loins|strong=\"G3751\"of|strong=\"G5485\"your|strong=\"G1722\"mind|strong=\"G1271\"girt up, being|strong=\"G4771\"sober|strong=\"G3525\", trust|strong=\"G1679\"perfectly in|strong=\"G1722\"the|strong=\"G3588\"grace|strong=\"G5485\"which|strong=\"G3588\"is|strong=\"G3588\"offered you|strong=\"G5210\"in|strong=\"G1722\"the|strong=\"G3588\"revelation|strong=\"G0602\"of|strong=\"G5485\"Jesus|strong=\"G2424\"Christ|strong=\"G5547\",",
