      "1": "Wherefore laying|strong=\"G0659\"away all|strong=\"G3956\"malice|strong=\"G2549\", and|strong=\"G2532\"all|strong=\"G3956\"guile, and|strong=\"G2532\"dissimulations, and|strong=\"G2532\"envies, and|strong=\"G2532\"all|strong=\"G3956\"detractions,",
