      "17": "Honour all|strong=\"G3956\"men|strong=\"G3956\". Love|strong=\"G0025\"the|strong=\"G3956\"brotherhood|strong=\"G0081\". Fear|strong=\"G5399\"God|strong=\"G2316\". Honour the|strong=\"G3956\"king|strong=\"G0935\".",
      "18": "Servants, be|strong=\"G2532\"subject|strong=\"G5293\"to|strong=\"G2532\"your|strong=\"G2532\"masters|strong=\"G1203\"with|strong=\"G1722\"all|strong=\"G3956\"fear|strong=\"G5401\", not|strong=\"G3756\"only|strong=\"G3440\"to|strong=\"G2532\"the|strong=\"G3956\"good|strong=\"G0018\"and|strong=\"G2532\"gentle|strong=\"G1933\", but|strong=\"G0235\"also|strong=\"G2532\"to|strong=\"G2532\"the|strong=\"G3956\"froward.",
      "19": "For|strong=\"G1063\"this|strong=\"G3778\"is|strong=\"G2316\"thankworthy, if|strong=\"G1487\"for|strong=\"G1063\"conscience|strong=\"G4893\"towards God|strong=\"G2316\", a|strong=\"G1487\"man|strong=\"G3778\"endure|strong=\"G5297\"sorrows|strong=\"G3077\", suffering|strong=\"G3958\"wrongfully.",
      "20": "For|strong=\"G1063\"what|strong=\"G4169\"glory is|strong=\"G2316\"it|strong=\"G3778\", if|strong=\"G1487\"committing|strong=\"G0264\"sin|strong=\"G0264\", and|strong=\"G2532\"being buffeted for|strong=\"G1063\"it|strong=\"G3778\", you|strong=\"G1487\"endure|strong=\"G5278\"? But|strong=\"G0235\"if|strong=\"G1487\"doing|strong=\"G0015\"well|strong=\"G2532\"you|strong=\"G1487\"suffer|strong=\"G3958\"patiently|strong=\"G5278\"; this|strong=\"G3778\"is|strong=\"G2316\"thankworthy before|strong=\"G3844\"God|strong=\"G2316\".",
